path  - (Optional) Path to the ROS workspace to mount. Must be absolute.
        Default: . (current folder)
        Example: /home/username/my_ws

Reset the sr-dev docker container. It will base the container on the image whose
name is:
  - given by the SR_IMAGE_NAME environment variable if it is set
  - cyrillg/sr-dev if it is not
The <path> will be mounted as a shared volume in the container as /home/serial/ros-ws.
